subject: Dogs
Westminster Kennel Club Dog Show
lead_paragraph: About 225 dogs competed Saturday at the Masters Agility Championship, an inaugural Westminster Kennel Club event that, unlike the best-in-show contest, was open to mixed-breed entrants.
